        Called when a projectile is set to move towards a point. For projectiles that target the ground, like AoE projectiles from Lizardman Shamans, this is only called once

        targetX - X position of where the projectile is being moved to
        targetY - Y position of where the projectile is being moved to
        targetZ - Z position of where the projectile is being moved to
        cycle -

      • onActorHitsplat

        public static void onActorHitsplat(Actor actor,
                                   int type,
                                   int value,
                                   int var3,
                                   int var4,
                                   int gameCycle,
                                   int duration)
        Called after a hitsplat has been processed on an actor. Note that this event runs even if the hitsplat didn't show up, i.e. the actor already had 4 visible hitsplats.
        Parameters:
        actor - The actor the hitsplat was applied to
        type - The hitsplat type (i.e. color)
        value - The value of the hitsplat (i.e. how high the hit was)
        var3 -
        var4 -
        gameCycle - The gamecycle the hitsplat was applied on
        duration - The amount of gamecycles the hitsplat will last for
